{"tid":1242254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］有關二十一號嘅焦點","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:13:12.000Z","uid":155837,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2638da1bf15b7cd5e33d4ddc908862d086249a62","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家一盤散沙嘅其中一個原因係因為我地焦點散左，市民冇左一個<span style=\"color: red;\">逼切嘅原因同理由</span>出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n原本四大訴求<br />\n1.撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2.取消暴動定性<br />\n3.釋放被捕人士<br />\n4.追究黑警責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n其實如果佢依家夠膽重推，一定多過200萬人上街，一定更多人發夢去衝，國際社會一定會睇唔過眼。短期內，我要強調係短期內，佢係唔會再推呢個修訂。 再加上有好多市民開始認為林鄭只係唔方便講撤回，其實依家已經當係撤回左。<br />\n我地要諗嘅就係，我地係咪仲要用反送中去做我地嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一訴求</span>，呢個訴求會唔會其實已經得唔得市民嘅認同？值得討論。<br />\n<br />\n2.取消暴動定性<br />\n警務處長語言藝術話得五個人暴動，有好多市民都不滿，咁即係話每人平均食三十粒催淚彈，四粒子彈。另外有律師指出，就算佢話五個人係暴動罪，咁其實同定性成件事係暴動冇分別。<br />\n我地要諗嘅就係，係咪應該將呢個訴求<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發大黎搞</span>，做更多嘅宣傳。而2-4入面，依個訴求亦都係可行性最大。<br />\n<br />\n3.釋放被捕人士<br />\n琴日無條件放左八個人，但有議員指出係可以隨時拉返，文宣組係咪應該要係依方面多加宣傳？令更多市民了解真相。同埋係咪應該要指出我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個都不能少</span>，去振奮士氣呢？<br />\n<br />\n4.追究黑警責任<br />\n依個係人神共憤嘅野（講緊嘅係就算中遊派都好嬲黑警），開槍爆頭，打鬧記者，150粒催淚彈... 文宣係咪應該開始要再提下啲黑警有幾黑？等大家有一定嘅怒氣值去出黎。"},{"pid":"a40b5c9916fb4024b2ec535be061264a8a96582e","tid":1242254,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a72bb30638c025dbb75097e5fe1c8cd4ec7bb22","tid":1242254,"uid":263261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ccdf1a9194f7aee3e433188e3a018447f3be33","tid":1242254,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b25eb0c889346c51969d967c9b274be478a37455","tid":1242254,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6549d5369b265e69588e382005eeb40d56275130","tid":1242254,"uid":7760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該將解除暴動定性放首位<br />\n之後就放人<br />\n第三追究黑警<br />\n最後先係撤回<br />\n<br />\n明白義士被捕好慘<br />\n但今日放你出黎, 他日又用番暴動罪黎告又係仆街<br />\n政府好興等人民無再留意件事就郁手<br />\n<br />\n推啦 各位巴絲打講下意見<br />\n集中, 目標一致, 做左二十號二十一號既野先<br />\n選舉, 真普選, 蛇齋餅糭係之後既事"},{"pid":"66fddb13d278254e1204ee9373c823a1aabc9940","tid":1242254,"uid":7760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"推post 係好, 但都俾下意見, 依加未有結論, 一味推post 都係唔會有結論"},{"pid":"c9483ac31dfb3711696ca9d649c9fe5df049844f","tid":1242254,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果再用反送中做焦點 未必再受廣大市民支持<br />\n<br />\n如果用黑警嘅武力做焦點 會令市民更同情年輕人"},{"pid":"79a5a3a0cd38750953bf5795b73b991f3e3643a1","tid":1242254,"uid":70423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"第三點同第四點做主打啦。 <br />\n<br />\n同埋即刻少左好多人出都唔緊要，今次應該得返最核心既抗爭者會出現。 <br />\n<br />\n而且千萬要避免有衝突，當日點都唔係一個決戰既時機。"},{"pid":"a5c833011397b3038d12f7a6cb32a0c4b797a0fe","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當大家都好攰嘅時候，我地更需要一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強而有力</span></span>嘅原因去繼續行落去，可以係義士嘅以死相諫，可以係唔辜負被捕嘅義士..<br />\n<br />\n好多好多原因，但係香港人係善忘，所以先要靠大家同文宣組去提其他人: 其實要出黎嘅原因<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一直都喺到</span></span>，只係我地唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d86efb7bfe7c54d9a85a8104f2f22d7e02a07d4","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6549d5369b265e69588e382005eeb40d56275130","tid":1242254,"uid":7760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該將解除暴動定性放首位<br />\n之後就放人<br />\n第三追究黑警<br />\n最後先係撤回<br />\n<br />\n明白義士被捕好慘<br />\n但今日放你出黎, 他日又用番暴動罪黎告又係仆街<br />\n政府好興等人民無再留意件事就郁手<br />\n<br />\n推啦 各位巴絲打講下意見<br />\n集中, 目標一致, 做左二十號二十一號既野先<br />\n選舉, 真普選, 蛇齋餅糭係之後既事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"我認同依個順序，原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n暴動定性同埋放人有絕對嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逼切性</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n而追究黑警，就有極大嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意基礎</span></span>，我地打住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷者申冤</span></span>嘅旗號，絕對係一個強而有力嘅原因俾市民去出黎。"},{"pid":"658fd89827af27401b776df7f0dee3737abe492d","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1648304ce5922394b219cd60aa20a57fb44bb421","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec152f0f84d905614c4184baf13a0667d3d68c4","tid":1242254,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d500f4689b42203a45d9aa483e5153948d94889","tid":1242254,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d86efb7bfe7c54d9a85a8104f2f22d7e02a07d4","tid":1242254,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6549d5369b265e69588e382005eeb40d56275130","tid":1242254,"uid":7760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該將解除暴動定性放首位<br />\n之後就放人<br />\n第三追究黑警<br />\n最後先係撤回<br />\n<br />\n明白義士被捕好慘<br />\n但今日放你出黎, 他日又用番暴動罪黎告又係仆街<br />\n政府好興等人民無再留意件事就郁手<br />\n<br />\n推啦 各位巴絲打講下意見<br />\n集中, 目標一致, 做左二十號二十一號既野先<br />\n選舉, 真普選, 蛇齋餅糭係之後既事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"我認同依個順序，原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n暴動定性同埋放人有絕對嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逼切性</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n而追究黑警，就有極大嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意基礎</span></span>，我地打住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷者申冤</span></span>嘅旗號，絕對係一個強而有力嘅原因俾市民去出黎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"係呀 , 義士點都唔應該俾人用暴動黎告"},{"pid":"b8d0e604bff0de72f4eb3de85c01cb16b0a01014","tid":1242254,"uid":264945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"認同，另外行動地點需唔需要轉？星期五立法會唔審明日大嶼，會唔會去律政司或者警總好啲？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190618/59730373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59730373&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=f10ae84a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190618%2F59730373&h=925b2795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190618/59730373</a>"},{"pid":"03c89983c88272d06b431db39f29aa2285322879","tid":1242254,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9008e9f7a7765caa0128b5f15b53f3aff07422","tid":1242254,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"750b031616d2ef761a493f257e23a61ba968eba9","tid":1242254,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cbd9ce75261aa0dc8f6a04a800501e6e9498b8","tid":1242254,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"送中其實大家口講唔接受，好多都默默接受，諗住等佢再推先再反過。所以我覺得暴動論+不追究重要，一來唔可以睇住義士俾人拉，二來佢唔撤回=會秋後算賬，入到=以後唔駛野餐。之後係警方過份武力，因為佢單單野都有軟到少少唯太呢單死口唔認，堅持係適當，明顯想提高條底線下次跟足呢種程度嚟打！"},{"pid":"6b0708df387a1e807e70be453a62a233956fd457","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b689327c9b53e3ad23750b9589257cd8d942dd1","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b061f0e6c849ecb662d29c57108bc933435d71","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb93af894c1e9f971f1ac980e44f7050568ad59","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bbc27a5e4e7ee2042650de6b9501899e9283aa","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81ade50138687102d5cfdec59c028f2ad1eb517","tid":1242254,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":